title: [Solhaven, Bayside Road]
description: Bayside Road widens here, as throngs of people head southward into the North Market.  More than a few are drawn by the mouthwatering aroma of fresh-baked goods wafting from the doorway of the half-timber building opposite the bridge.  To the northwest, the Market Bridge spans the bay, heading towards Marshtown.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, east, south, southwest, northwest
